column2: "Impressive how well you fight with that trash, but wouldn't you say it's time to surrender, child?"
"...and again. I'm not used to such fragile weapons, but this is ridiculous."
"J-just how much potential is this girl hiding...!?"
"Something wrong? Now's your chance. Summon more of those darkers - I'll kill 'em all!"
"Fufu... Hahahaha! That expression! I was dying to see it!"
"I put on a good show, wouldn't you say? The trouble was worth it."
"Behold! The true power of Apprentice! I suppose you could call it my natural charm?"
"Now it's time for Round Two! Are you ready?"
"Let's see how the Darker Exterminator faces off against her own kind!!"
